title: Ep. - 298 - TINSLEY MORTIMER LIFE OF DOLLY PARTON
description:
Tinsley Mortimer talks about leaving Real Housewives of New York and starting a new chapter of her life in Chicago. She talks about her wedding plans and growing her family, how she looks back at this last season of filming, and how being part of the ensemble show changed the trajectory of her life.

 

Lydia Hamessley is the Author of Unlikely Angel: The Songs of Dolly Parton and featured in the Netflix documentary Dolly Parton: Here I Am. She talks about the life of Dolly Parton, the stories behind many of her hit songs, and her legacy.
